4 SECTION 2. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 2402,
5 is amended to read as follows:
6 Section 2402. A. There is hereby created the Oklahoma
7 State Regents' Academic Rising Scholars Award Program. The
8 purpose of the Oklahoma State Regents' Academic Rising
9 Scholars Award Program is to retain top-ranked students from
10 Oklahoma in Oklahoma colleges, enable Oklahoma institutions
11 of higher education to compete aggressively for top Oklahoma
12 scholars, attract high-caliber out-of-state students to
13 Oklahoma to attend colleges and universities, and enhance the
14 academic quality in Oklahoma colleges and universities. The
15 program shall provide participants funding for enrollment
16 fees, tuition and other fees, room and board and required
17 textbooks or materials for up to five (5) years of
18 undergraduate and/or graduate study at accredited
19 institutions of higher education in Oklahoma.
20 B. The Oklahoma State Regents for Higher Education shall
21 administer the provisions of the Oklahoma State Regents' Academic
22 Rising Scholars Award Program.
