12 SECTION 4. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 2404, is
13 amended to read as follows:
14 Section 2404. A. Scholarships awarded under the Oklahoma State
15 Regents' Academic Rising Scholars Award Program shall be awarded to
16 all eligible applicants without any limitation on the number of
17 scholarships to be awarded in any year other than the amount of
18 funds available for the scholarship program and the number of
19 eligible applicants.
20 B. The Oklahoma State Regents for Higher Education may, at the
21 time a scholarship is awarded to a student, set aside in the
22 Oklahoma State Regents' Academic Rising Scholars Award Trust Fund
23 funds for the full five-year commitment made to such eligible
24 scholar. For all academic years, students who have previously
Req. No. 12529 Page 8

