2 who have continued at all times to fulfill the requirements for
3 eligibility to receive academic scholarships provided in this act
4 shall be given an absolute priority for continued financial support
5 by the Oklahoma State Regents' Academic Rising Scholars Award
6 Program superior to any students who are applying for such academic
7 scholarships awards for the first time.
